    "ğŸ‘‰ *BIG RULE:* No messing with others during their sales/missions â€” griefers will face consequences.\n"
    "ğŸ‘¥ *IMPORTANT:* The host will NOT add you. YOU must add them in-game so they can invite you to the lobby.\n"
